{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5e80a0e1f4","title":"中专教师的右派言论（一）","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4d72dd14a7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"323f974700","name":"李长之"},{"id":"695497a0d1","name":"高元江"},{"id":"7045192b52","name":"王化堂"},{"id":"c5c819f1d2","name":"朔风"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"383fbfe9dc","type":"title","text":"中专教师的右派言论（一）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"5fff113f1f","type":"authors","text":"山西朔风王化堂李鸿仁高元江","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"dd772604e3","type":"paragraph","text":"朔风（省建筑工程学校教师）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"0e483518bf","type":"paragraph","text":"“今后用人应是唯材主义。因解放几年来，旧知识分子得到了不少改造，和共产党员差不多了，因此应实行用人唯材主义”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"37da361ce3","type":"paragraph","text":"王化堂（机械工业学校教师）：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"88d3e87014","type":"paragraph","text":"“百分之七十的农民并不愿入社，是共产党硬宣传起来的，干部开会开的，因此，搞得太快了，农民没有积极性，增产二百亿斤粮食不确实”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"f19a4d06ba","type":"paragraph","text":"李鸿仁（机械工业学校教师）：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"0801861eac","type":"paragraph","text":"“农民生活不如解放前好了，现在是要啥无啥，从古至今没有吃过360斤粮食，都没有像现在吃不饱”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"92ced3213e","type":"paragraph","text":"高元江（太原工业学校教师）：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"},{"id":"1c25d29cd4","type":"paragraph","text":"“农民生活就是没有提高，好多农民不愿卖粮，干部非叫卖不行，有的农民因此自杀，但自杀了也得卖，总之，农民很苦，老是吞糠嚥菜”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4"}],"page":{"id":"f4890c3bfe","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e80a0e1f4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}